      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Runs and drives, but this is an honest rough-condition vehicle being sold as a budget car or project. Expect noticeable cosmetic wear, body and paint imperfections, and an interior that shows heavy use. It is not a clean or turnkey example, and buyers should plan on deferred maintenance, age-related issues, and repairs to bring it up to a higher standard. Best suited for someone looking for inexpensive transportation, a fixer-upper, or parts depending on their needs.",
