    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Affordable driver-quality classic with great style and a solid, honest presence. This is a fair-condition car that shows age and wear, but it still has good appeal for someone who wants a usable vintage car to enjoy as-is while improving over time. A nice opportunity to get into a classic without paying show-car money.",
