    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Value-focused and priced to move, this vehicle is a practical option for buyers seeking affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who appreciates a straightforward, budget-conscious purchase, but it still offers the core utility and presence that make it worth a look. An honest offering with real potential for the right owner.",
