    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic wheels, a project, or a handy spare. It\u2019s being offered honestly as-is, and with a little care, it could make a great everyday runabout or starter fixer-upper. If you want something inexpensive and straightforward, this could be a really worthwhile buy.",
